&lt;div class=&#34;note&#34;&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
        In &lt;i&gt;Rating&lt;/i&gt;,&lt;br&gt;
        V refers to Visual effects;&lt;br&gt;
        S refers to Sound effects;&lt;br&gt;
        P refers to Plots;&lt;br&gt;
        C refers to the design of Characters;&lt;br&gt;
        ❤ refers to my Love for the anime, of course.&lt;br&gt;
